msgstr "That too is a way to understand how extinguishment is bliss."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an9.34:5.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sukhassa ca pahānā … pe … catutthaṃ jhānaṃ "
"upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a mendicant who, giving up pleasure and pain, and ending "
"former happiness and sadness, enters and remains in the fourth absorption."

msgctxt "an9.34:5.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa ce, āvuso, bhikkhuno iminā vihārena viharato upekkhāsahagatā "
"saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti, svassa hoti ābādho."
msgstr ""
"While a mendicant is in such a meditation, should perceptions and attentions "
"accompanied by equanimous bliss beset them, that’s an affliction for them."

msgctxt "an9.34:5.3"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, āvuso, sukhino dukkhaṃ uppajjeyya yāvadeva ābādhāya;"
