#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an9.34:7.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sabbaso ākāsānañcāyatanaṃ samatikkamma anantaṃ "
"viññāṇanti viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of "
"infinite space, aware that ‘consciousness is infinite’, enters and remains "
"in the dimension of infinite consciousness."

msgctxt "an9.34:7.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa ce, āvuso, bhikkhuno iminā vihārena viharato ākāsānañcāyatanasahagatā "
"saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti, svassa hoti ābādho."
msgstr ""
"While a mendicant is in such a meditation, should perceptions and attentions "
"accompanied by the dimension of infinite space beset them, that’s an "
"affliction for them."

msgctxt "an9.34:7.3"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, āvuso, sukhino dukkhaṃ uppajjeyya yāvadeva ābādhāya;"
msgstr ""
