msgstr "That too is a way to understand how extinguishment is bliss."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an9.34:9.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sabbaso ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma "
"nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of "
"nothingness, enters and remains in the dimension of neither perception nor "
"non-perception."

msgctxt "an9.34:9.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa ce, āvuso, bhikkhuno iminā vihārena viharato ākiñcaññāyatanasahagatā "
"saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti, svassa hoti ābādho."
msgstr ""
"While a mendicant is in such a meditation, should perceptions and attentions "
"accompanied by the dimension of nothingness beset them, that’s an affliction "
"for them."

msgctxt "an9.34:9.3"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, āvuso, sukhino dukkhaṃ uppajjeyya yāvadeva ābādhāya;"
msgstr ""
"Suppose a happy person were to experience pain; that would be an affliction "
"for them."

msgctxt "an9.34:9.4"
msgid ""
"evamevassa te ākiñcaññāyatanasahagatā saññāmanasikārā samudācaranti. Svassa "
"hoti ābādho."
msgstr ""
